HEADWORD: Testudinarious
<hw>Tes*tu`di*na"ri*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the shell of a tortoise;
resembling a tortoise shell; having the color or markings of a tortoise
shell.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Testudinata</ent>⟦br⟧
